        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> Just curious.  When grouped or even solo'ing, how often do you swap out spells?  When I'm grouped I seem to be CONSTANTLY swapping out my spells for other things.  One second I need arch lich, the next screaming terror, then I gotta swap out for 2 dots,then uh oh time to heal the main tank..ect..ect..</P><P>Is there a fast way to do this? Some hotkey I can set up??  Or does everyone hit there dotp(dotpage) hotkey to open their book and swap spells really quickly like I do?</P><P> </font></td>

