        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         <BR>Only thing you can do to help is to arrange the spellbook in a nice way. I have commonly used spells such as levant, FD, gate, DMF, pet buff etc on page 1-2. Then I have a hotkey panel to access the other pages with hotkeys rather than having to browse the spellbook. </P><P>Works rather well, even though I think it's super-lame that we still have only 8 spell slots despite 3 expansions and tons of new spells at our disposal.</P><P><BR>Zarloth V`Sharatouum<BR>Teir`dal Warlock<BR>Vallon Zek<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=61907" target="_blank">Magelo</a><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
