        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I have a similar setup.</P><P>My last page of hotkeys (CTRL 0 or whatever) is set up /page1 /page3 /page 5 on down the line.  I can flip between pages in my book with a keystroke.</P><P>My first page is my normal set of spells memed, <BR>Page two is stuff I can cast to benefit others (DMF, twitch, Shadowbond lineup, bind, etc...) also lich and bond of death on the bottom.<BR>Page three is all my pet related stuff<BR>Page four is my vs. undead stuff (charm / undead nuke / invis vs. ud)<BR>Page five is all my heavy dots.</P><P>After that it is just sort of random but I remember where they are.</P><P>As for fast swapouts, none that I know of - you are already doing it best way I know how.</P><P>Glonoin</P><P>Using your dead bodies to create a better tomorrow..<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
