        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         i generally plan out my fighting style so I won't have to swap. Three slots for survival spells, one or two slots for crowd control, one or two slots for healing (lifetap or vex) and the remaining 1-3 slots for whatever I think I'm going to need, usually damage dealers.</P><P>I do have a hotkey system that can let me get to any type of spell quickly so if I have to swap I can do it, but again I try to avoid it.</P><P>Only situations where I find myself regularly swapping spells is when I'm charm soloing, I exchange thrall and pyro quite often depending on whether I have a pet charmed or not.</P><P><a href="http://xzzy.org/ereet/" target="_blank">http://xzzy.org/ereet/</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
