        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I hate being CC but i love being a healer in a group.  Its easy to cast Vex or BoD then heal the tanks and cast a splurt too.  I have done it a few times in frenzy groups up in Velks.  I have a smaller death rate than most clerics thats for sure.  I have a friend now that invites me into the group when they are looking for a cleric.  I still don't trust ST enough to be a chanter.</P><P>Darque Evilfro 58th <BR>Begger of the 200th Copper <BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=226497" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=226497</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
