        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=37555&amp;TOPIC_ID=4676&amp;FORUM_ID=2&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=General+Discussions&amp;Topic_Title=Art+of+Spell+Swapping&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Zeefers really is awesome.. it can totally replace your Vexing Mordania. Occasionally you may want to ToN or Deflux to catch it up, but we're talking like once every 20+ minutes or so. .Zeefers does take a lot of mana, but the power it gives us is amazing.. I do give Verant kudos on giving us this spell, but completely believe that they didn't realize how powerful it was.. otherwise they wouldn't have given it to us or would have reduced it's effect.</P><P>Anyway, as for the Insidious.. three reasons.<BR>1) It costs 210 mana'ish, less than cascading darkness (300mana).<BR>2) The slow on it slows them to about the same crawl as our 59 darkness.<BR>3) It does 560'ish damage in one shot. So it's more mana efficient than IB/CB/etc for nuking purposes, and it does it all in one shot as opposed to darkness. (Why cast 300 mana and a darkness on something that your group might finish off in 20 seconds?) Half the time, if you time it right (about 1/3 - 1/4 the mobs health), the damage from Insidious will finish the mob off. And if it doesn't quite finish him off, woo! He's snared for your group.</P><P>It was a change for me to start using it a while back as I used to love our 59 darkness (I used it mostly for the damage, the snare was just a nice bonus). But in places like Sebilis, 400mana a pop for something that the rogue in your group might assassinate in .03 seconds more of fighting is kinda silly.</P><P>If you already have your epic, this then isn't really a necessary tactic (although since Insidious resists on poison, it's a very viable alternative in some situations).</P><P></P><P><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=205091" target="_blank"><font color=red><font size=5>Ashtaroth Solarium</font id=size5></font id=red></a><BR><i>Nec-Romancer of Innoruuk</i><BR><i>Legends of the Realm</i><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
